### ===================================================
### Sync endpoints
### ===================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Login first
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Get connection status
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/connection-status
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get sync stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Trigger manual sync (upstream - outbox)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sync/trigger
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Retry failed events
POST {{baseUrl}}/sync/retry-failed
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Sync from central (downstream - pull episodes)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sync/from-central
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}
